title: Jarvan Main Club
body:
Hey guys,
I was searching a club for  {{champion:59}}  mains but  i didnt found any of those clubs. So i thought it would be a idea to create my own {{champion:59}} main clan. If you are a {{champion:59}} main and interested for a club with other mains to discuss some new builds or something, ad me. Your welcome!{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

replies.body: Hey ich Jarvan Main insgesamt 300.000 Punkte und würde da gerne beitreten wen noch ein Platz frei ist lg Jarvan For The Win xD{{sticker:sg-lulu}}

Hey it would  be nice if  u add me ingame, so that i can invite  u into the club ;) I wish u a lot of fun
